{"title":"咱们是一家人了","authors":["黄炎培"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":2,"day":10}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们是一家人了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄炎培"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（邢台县火焰农业合作社下放干部孟征祥1957年12月28日来信，节取它的词句写成一首诗。）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我开始干活了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我在前炉子村住。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社里为我布置得很好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我和社员们拥抱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有说有笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们是一家人了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"紧紧结合，打成一片。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"接受共产党的领导，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家走上社会主义光明大道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民是种什么、吃什么的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平时小米磨面，天天吃饱。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"支援国家工业建设，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还卖出余粮不少。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在吃到大米饭了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家欢呼著："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠毛主席的福，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"靠共产党领导。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"整天抬土，不觉得苦恼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"右肩压得又红又肿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在困难已经克服了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"乡长对我说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"时候还早，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为今后农忙打下基础，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要把双手锻炼得粗糙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我做新农民了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民艰苦朴素，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"待人诚恳周到，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阶级立场是鲜明的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大大地帮助我改造。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我虚心向农民学习："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习农民的阶级本质；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学习农业生产技术。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"经过劳动锻炼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脱胎换骨地改造。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家拿出革命干劲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掀起农业生产高潮。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}